title: Blueberry courgette cake
ingredients: ['3 eggs, lightly beaten', '250ml vegetable oil', '3 teaspoons vanilla extract', '450g caster sugar', '250g grated courgette', '375g plain flour', '1 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1/4 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 tablespoon ground cinnamon', '325g fresh blueberries']
